verbs.description: iran summons [V: danish] [ARG0: envoy] over alleged deadly tehran plot iran on wednesday summoned the danish ambassador to tehran over copenhagen allegations about an iranian plot to kill an opposition activist in denmark the official irna news agency reported iran expressed a strong protest to ambassador danny annan over what it described as the danish officials hasty political and uncalculated actions in the case the development came after denmark intelligence agency said on tuesday that a police operation last month that briefly cut off copenhagen from the rest of denmark stemmed from an alleged iranian plot to kill an opposition activist it said a suspect in the case a norwegian citizen of iranian descent has denied wrongdoing and is being held in pre - trial custody until nov 8 europe ministry of foreign affairs iran iran norway danny annan iranian foreign ministry ahvaz asmla tehran mike pompeo finn borch andersen copenhagen associated press plot iran foreign ministry denmark erna solberg service chief irans foreign ministry irna fox news arab struggle movement matthew lee
